OL,3,CMan arrested over woman's death in
OL,4,CDunmurry 'released unconditionally'
OL,6,FPolice have confirmed the sudden death
OL,7,Fof a woman in West Belfast on Saturday
OL,8,Fwas "not being treated as suspicious".
OL,10,FThe woman in her 40s was found dead at
OL,11,Fa house in the Helen's Wood Court area
OL,12,Fof Dunmurry.
OL,14,FA postmortem was carried on Monday and
OL,15,Fthe PSNI said a man who was arrested
OL,16,Fon Saturday night and questioned in
OL,17,Frelation to the death "has been
OL,18,Freleased unconditionally".
