OL,3,CMan arrested over woman's death in
OL,4,CDunmurry 'released unconditionally'
OL,6,FSinn Fein west Belfast MLA Orlaithi
OL,7,FFlynn said: "I am shocked and saddened
OL,8,Fto hear this death in Dunmurry. My
OL,9,Fimmediate thoughts are with this
OL,10,Findividual's family and friends. Their
OL,11,Fgrief will be immeasurable right now."
